uh, Darcy's intern.

990
01:11:42,298 --> 01:11:44,471
Yeah, I don't get paid either.

991
01:11:45,343 --> 01:11:46,811
Are you all right?

992
01:11:46,969 --> 01:11:48,812
I've had a God in my brain.

993
01:11:50,139 --> 01:11:51,607
