1026
01:14:36,681 --> 01:14:37,773
dead at my feet!

1027
01:14:41,268 --> 01:14:42,315
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

1028
01:14:45,606 --> 01:14:46,607
<font color="#808080">(MOANING)</font>

1029
01:14:48,901 --> 01:14:49,993
<font color="#808080">(GASPS)</font>

1030
01:14:50,403 --> 01:14:51,404
Malekith!

1031
01:14:53,489 --> 01:14:55,491
